sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Ops as Operatör eller Logic App
    participant APIM as APIM
    participant CF as Common Function App
    participant SB as Service Bus Topic Subscription
    participant LA as Log Analytics

    Ops->>APIM: POST GetTopicSubscriptionDeferredMessagesPeek
    APIM->>CF: HTTP trigger
    CF->>SB: Peek deferred messages
    SB-->>CF: Lista deferred messages
    CF-->>APIM: 200 + deferred lista
    APIM-->>Ops: Deferred översikt

    Ops->>APIM: POST GetTopicSubscriptionDeferredMessagePeek sequenceNumber
    APIM->>CF: HTTP trigger
    CF->>SB: Peek specifikt deferred message
    SB-->>CF: Message eller MessageNotFound
    CF-->>Ops: 200 eller MessageNotFound-status

    alt Action Complete
        Ops->>APIM: POST CompleteTopicDeferredMessage
        APIM->>CF: HTTP trigger
        CF->>SB: Complete deferred message
        SB-->>CF: Ack
        CF-->>Ops: 200
    else Action Abandon
        Ops->>APIM: POST AbandonTopicDeferredMessage
        APIM->>CF: HTTP trigger
        CF->>SB: Abandon deferred message
        SB-->>CF: Ack
        CF-->>Ops: 200
    else Action DeadLetter
        Ops->>APIM: POST DeadLetterTopicDeferredMessage reason
        APIM->>CF: HTTP trigger
        CF->>SB: Dead-letter deferred message
        SB-->>CF: Ack
        CF-->>Ops: 200
    end

    Note over CF,LA: DeadLetterTimerTracker kör dagligen 01:00 och skickar dead-letter-summering till Log Analytics.
